# a\(n\) \= n\!\*\(n\+1\)\!^3\.

## Sage
```Sage
def a(n): return factorial(n-1)*(factorial(n)**(4-1))
```
## Python
```Python
from math import factorial
def A371560(n): return factorial(n)**4*(n+1)**3 # _Chai Wah Wu_, Apr 22 2024
```
